title: All Filipino team looking for more players.
body: Add me up or leave your summoners name, no rank requirement but must have a Mic. Preferably must know how to speak Tagalog.

replies.body: Yo. I like 2 sign up. I'm filo and im plat 4. It's my 1st season 2 play league but i'm getting good at it. Didn't expect 2 reach plat 4 in my 1st season.
